HEADWORD: Ecbole
<hw>Ec"bo*le</hw> <pr>(⟦ecr⟧k"b⟦osl⟧*l⟦emac⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[NL., fr. Gr. <grk>'ekbolh`</grk> a throwing out, a digression, fr.
